TITLE: Configuring Session Expiration in Better Auth
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to configure session expiration settings in Better Auth. It sets the expiration period to 7 days and configures the session to be refreshed every day.
SOURCE: https://github.com/better-auth/better-auth/blob/main/docs/content/docs/concepts/session-management.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { betterAuth } from "better-auth"

export const auth = betterAuth({
    //... other config options
    session: {
        expiresIn: 60 * 60 * 24 * 7, // 7 days
        updateAge: 60 * 60 * 24 // 1 day (every 1 day the session expiration is updated)
    }
})
```

