TITLE: Implementing Forget Password Functionality in Better Auth
DESCRIPTION: Code sample demonstrating how to trigger the password reset process by calling the forgetPassword function with the user's email and a redirect URL.
SOURCE: https://github.com/better-auth/better-auth/blob/main/docs/content/docs/authentication/email-password.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const { data, error } = await authClient.forgetPassword({
  email: "test@example.com",
  redirectTo: "/reset-password",
});
```

