TITLE: Installing Better Auth
DESCRIPTION: This command installs the Better Auth package into your project. It is important to install the package in both the client and server if you have a separate setup.
SOURCE: https://github.com/better-auth/better-auth/blob/main/docs/content/docs/installation.mdx#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: txt
CODE:
```
