TITLE: Change User Email with Better Auth Client
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to use the `changeEmail` function on the Better Auth client to initiate the email change process. It requires the new email and a callback URL for redirection after verification.
SOURCE: https://github.com/better-auth/better-auth/blob/main/docs/content/docs/concepts/users-accounts.mdx#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
await authClient.changeEmail({
    newEmail: "new-email@email.com",
    callbackURL: "/dashboard", //to redirect after verification
});
```

